Java代码&nbsp;&nbsp; SET&nbsp;CATALINA_OPTS=-server&nbsp;-Xdebug&nbsp;-Xnoagent&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -Djava.compiler=NONE&nbsp;-Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=8000&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
